REPLACE ME.

Only place font files here that are licensed for embedding.

If licensed:
  qcap-heading.woff2         Display / headings
  qcap-body.woff2            Body copy
  qcap-mono.woff2            Numeric / code
  LICENSE                    Full font licence text (MANDATORY)

Otherwise (recommended default), QCAP uses the system font stack — no files
required.
